-- Peru sees 5.2 pct economic expansion in second half of 2014
-- By Teresa Cespedes
-- Thu Aug 14, 2014 10:34AM EDT
-- None



LIMA, Aug 14 (Reuters) - Peru's finance minister said on Thursday that the economy will likely rebound to grow by 5.2 percent in the second half of 2014 after appearing to expand by about 3.3 percent in the first six months of the year.

